Tk-FreeDesktop-Wm
=================

Tk::FreeDesktop::WM creates a bridge between freedesktop-compliant
window managers (see http://www.freedesktop.org/ ) and Perl/Tk
programs, providing information and manipulation methods.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

  Tk

